#

French Bistro Burger with Herb Garlic Butter and Gruyère Cheese

$18.5
900 kcal
Difficulty: 40%

Allergens:

DairyGluten

Dietary Tags:

Gluten-FreeHigh-Protein

Tags:

GourmetBurgerFrenchComfort Food

Description

Savor the rich flavors of a gourmet burger topped with savory herb garlic butter and melted Gruyère, paired with crispy sweet potato fries and luxurious truffle aioli.

Ingredients

  • Ground Beef: 1 lb
  • Brioche Buns: 2
  • Gruyère Cheese: 4 slices
  • Sweet Potatoes: 2 large
  • Olive Oil: 2 tbsp
  • Garlic: 3 cloves
  • Fresh Herbs (Thyme, Parsley): 1 tbsp each
  • Truffle Oil: 1 tbsp
  • Mayonnaise: 1/2 cup
  • Salt: to taste
  • Pepper: to taste
